definitions.definition: A white transparent waxy crystalline isoprenoid ketone , 1,7,7-trimethylbicyclo[2.2.1]heptan-2-one , with a strong pungent odour, used in pharmacy.

main_definition: ( organic chemistry ) A white transparent waxy crystalline isoprenoid ketone , 1,7,7-trimethylbicyclo[2.2.1]heptan-2-one , with a strong pungent odour, used in pharmacy.
